name: Shalom looks at me dissapointed V2
description:
Cat fix drawing series.
2877x2836
Shalom was the cat of a rich family but he was very neglected. He used to cry a lot until he moved with his sister to our aparment where he lives with my girlfriend, my girlfriend's sister, our three other cats and me. He's happy now but sometimes he looks at me like he's judging my choices.
